data.description: Very solid built home in a great setting. Views of Mt Elinor. This home sits at the end of a cul-de-sac which makes it very private. Laminated floors and a fair amount of living space. Lots of charm - come and take a look. Close to the lower lake which has great fishing. Come and take advantage of all Lake Cushman amenities. Propane tank is owned by the seller and will transfer to buyer with sale of the home. Home being sold as is.
